headline: HONEYWELL ANNOUNCES UPDATED BUSINESS SEGMENT STRUCTURE AHEAD OF AEROSPACE SPIN-OFF
summary: Honeywell (NASDAQ: HON) today announced its updated business segment structure ahead of the planned separation of its Aerospace Technologies business, expected in the second half of 2026, and its Solstice Advanced Materials business, expected to be completed on October 30, 2025.
